<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<title>id attribute of rbc element</title>
<style type="text/css">
rtc
	{visibility:hidden}
rtc#pass, rtc#passed
	{visibility:visible}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div><ruby><rbc><rb>a</rb></rbc><rtc id="pass"><rt>P</rt></rtc><rtc id="passed"><rt>S</rt></rtc></ruby></div>
<div>s</div>
<p>You should see word PASS above</p>
</body>
